<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038595" n="171r"/>
<p><lb/><del>Non respondi hactenus hucusque a </del>Distuli ad hoc usque tempus responsionem ad binas Tuas
                    <lb/><rs type="letters" key="B_1720-03-10_991170517025705501 B_1720-03-02_991170517025805501">litteras</rs> charissimas, in quibus <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me petiisti, ut <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationem</rs>
                    <lb/>Tuam cum a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">nÃÑ</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>otationibus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> mei per <rs type="person">Mercatorem</rs>
                    <lb/>aliquem transmittam vel <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3173435">Mediolanum</rs>  vel <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Bergomum</rs>;
                    <lb/>distuli, inquam, responsionem, quia sciebam instare redi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelis</rs> mei ad Vos, nullamque contra sciebam
                    <lb/>meliorem occasionem tibi transmittendi dictam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">disser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tationem</rs> Tuam doctissimam, quam per ipsum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patrue<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lem</rs> meum, qui crastina die hinc profecturus Deoque
                    <lb/>volente <add>eam</add> Tibi brevi allaturus est. Locutus sum de obje<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctione illa, quam aliqui formant contra opinionem
                    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-129832952">Co<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">nÃÑ</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ori</rs><supplied>,</supplied> <add><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs></add> aliorumque de secretionibus, cum ipso <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs>,
                    <lb/>qui ita <del>breviter </del>brevibus respondet: Humores pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terna<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>turales non ita verrere cavitates glandularum <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr>
                    <lb/>renalium durante morbo,<del> ita</del> ut in ejusmodi glandulis nihil
                    <lb/>urin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> remaneat, sed rem ita concipi posse, quod<del> humo</del>
                    <lb/>in statu pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ternaturali glandul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">√†</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vi morbi ita per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>forentur, ut una cum urina <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> transmittant etiam
                    <lb/>alios liquores, qui, si foramina fuerint<note type="editorial">Wortumstellung.</note> satis magna pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>polle<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bunt quoad quantitatem urin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, ita ut ista cum aliis <subst><del>per</del><add>liquo</add></subst><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><add>ribus</add> in parva quantitate permixta vix sentiri possit; cessante
                    <lb/>autem morbo iterum consolidantur ista foramina, glandu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que secernunt tantum modo<del> eum liquo</del> urinam, qua
                    <lb/><del>et </del>durante etiam morbo cavitates glandularum renalium
                    <lb/>semper imbut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fuerunt. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum gaudeo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruelem</rs> meum tua ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>citia <add>secunda vice</add> coram fruiturum esse, utque ipsi pariter atque mihi porro faveas,
                    <lb/>enixe rogo.</p> <closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline><abbr>Dab.</abbr> <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">√¶</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1720-04-11">11. Aprilis 1720</date>.</dateline><note type="editorial">Diese letzte Zeile befindet sich auf dem linken Rand der Seite.</note></closer>
</div>
